    <item>
      <title>商业地产压力迫使黑石抵押房地产投资信托基金削减股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/blackstone-mortgage-reit-bxmt-cuts-dividend-as-distress-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为商业房地产提供融资的黑石抵押信托公司 (Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc.) 将股息削减 24%，原因是违约率上升，而且借款人难以偿还贷款或进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/blackstone-mortgage-reit-bxmt-cuts-dividend-as-distress-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
