      <title>阿斯顿·马丁超级跑车受到富裕买家的强烈需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/aston-martin-sees-loss-widen-but-sticks-to-annual-guidance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯顿·马丁Lagonda Global Holdings Plc 的高价限量版汽车需求强劲，帮助这家英国汽车制造商提高了平均售价并抵消了交付量下降的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/aston-martin-sees-loss-widen-but-sticks-to-annual-guidance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
